      DESC="libIDL is Library for creating trees of COBRA IDL files.
libIDL is a library for creating trees of
CORBA Interface Definition Language (IDL) files,
which is a specification for defining portable interfaces.
libIDL was initially written for ORBit
(the ORB from the GNOME project,
and the primary means of libIDL distribution)."
